==English==

===Adverb===
'''according as'''
#[[precisely]] as; the same as; corresponding to the way in which. 
#:*Is all things well, '''According as''' I gave directions? - Shakespeare, ''2 Henry VI, III-ii''
#:*The land which the Lord will give you '''according as''' he hath promised. - ''Exodus 12:25''

====Usage note====
'''According as''' is an [[adverbial]] phrase, of which the [[propriety]] has been doubted; but good usage [[sanctions]] it.

